🔹 Q1: Tell me about yourself (MOST IMPORTANT)

👉 Structure (Follow strictly):

Introduction
Education
Skills
Strengths
Career goal
✅ PERFECT ANSWER (PLACEMENT LEVEL)
Writing

My name is Akshay. I am currently pursuing my engineering in Electrical and Electronics Engineering. I have a strong interest in technology, especially in areas like AI, cloud computing, and cybersecurity.

I have been consistently working on improving my aptitude, logical reasoning, and communication skills to prepare for placements. I also have basic knowledge of programming and problem-solving.

I am a disciplined and quick learner, and I enjoy taking on challenges that help me grow. My goal is to start my career in a reputed company where I can learn, contribute, and build strong technical expertise.

🔹 Q2: What are your strengths?

👉 Never say generic answers ❌
👉 Give proof-based answers ✅

✅ SAMPLE ANSWER
Writing

One of my key strengths is consistency. I have been preparing daily for placements by improving my aptitude, reasoning, and communication skills.

I am also a quick learner, which helps me adapt to new concepts and technologies easily. Additionally, I have good problem-solving skills and I stay calm under pressure, which helps me perform better in challenging situations.

🔹 Q3: What are your weaknesses?

👉 Don’t say “no weakness” ❌
👉 Show improvement mindset ✅

✅ SAMPLE ANSWER
Writing

One area I am currently working on is overthinking while solving problems. Sometimes I spend extra time analyzing a question.

However, I am actively improving this by practicing regularly and focusing on time management during mock tests.

🔹 Q4: Why should we hire you?

👉 Show value + confidence

✅ SAMPLE ANSWER
Writing

I believe I am a strong fit for this role because I have been consistently preparing myself in aptitude, logical reasoning, and communication skills.

I am a quick learner, disciplined, and highly motivated to grow. I am ready to take responsibility, learn new technologies, and contribute effectively to the team.

